{"tid":1032862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★自煮硏發！華為Router Q2 Pro將預售：搭載自研 \"凌霄電力貓芯片\"","createTime":"2019-02-22T16:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T12:59:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8f30529b6bcee8a828bb9f09f0dd57647f4314b4","tid":1032862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"IT之家2月22日消息華為今天官方宣布，華為路由Q2 Pro將開啟預售，支持千兆子母路由，搭載<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自研凌霄電力貓芯片，PLC Turbo黑科技加持</span></strong>，200M光纖寬帶高速擴展全家。華為路由Q2 Pro將在2月25日上午10點開啟預售，3月5日上午10點正式開售，目前售價和具體配置還未公佈<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2019/2/20190222_224844_748.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2019%2F2%2F20190222_224844_748.jpg&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLX%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=65b4b0b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2019/2/20190222_224844_748.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n去年5月份，華為子母路由器Q2隨華為P20系列機型一同發布，支持全千兆、最大1拖15、無損覆蓋全家等特性。實現百兆光纖無損覆蓋全家。其所搭載的華為凌霄自研千兆電力貓芯片5630，使得G.hn 1Gbps和家庭骨幹網絡延時小於10ms。<br />\n<br />\n功能方面，華為研發的智能WiFi能夠為用戶自動連接最佳信號，可以在多個路由之間進行無縫漫遊、真雙頻5G優選，切換時間在100ms內。<br />\n<br />\n華為路由Q2 Pro的具體更多信息還需在後續公佈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/410/804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F410%2F804.htm&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLX%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=fe1fcd32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/410/804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d9f8fb76a771f187dfb42e097e5c07ec2e68302c","tid":1032862,"uid":220701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"今次抄邊間？"},{"pid":"64cff30fdadda9cb4d4fb684405d573be73b7b6c","tid":1032862,"uid":65186,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"仲夠膽用？華為講明一直有比開資料中国政府"},{"pid":"e4befc320b31fff48bb4de6ed3eb87da75c6e031","tid":1032862,"uid":10757,"like":7,"d